From 845b23974cd49a467312fc7df7f2376e4dd3b28c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: sahbot <support.opensource@softathome.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 2025 19:19:29 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] fix: Fix Firewall_Enable chains (PPW-207)

Problem: When the firewall was disabled, the packets were still
being blocked.

Cause: It was missinng the FORWARD_Firewall_Enable chains

Solution: Add missing chains to netfilter, to make sure all
packets are being accepted.

Issue: PPW-207 - Firewall Enable
Signed-off-by: Lucas Vecchete <lucas.vecchete@softathome.com>
